, 156.6842, 157.6762, 156.411, 157.286, 157.6739, 157.4291, 157.984, 157.8259, 158.5294, 158.3784, 157.4018, 159.2213, 158.5818, 158.4016, 161.7159, 162.1593, 162.7058, 162.6404, 163.9899, 163.5, 164.8344, 164.1674, 163.7155, 162.6071, 163.9408, 163.663, 163.8422, 165.4323, 163.9927, 164.7716, 164.5866, 163.9004, 164.2766, 163.6699, 163.9126, 163.7993, 163.536, 166.1387, 166.7842, 167.1212, 168.2473, 168.4631, 169.1431, 169.4861, 168.169, 168.3575, 168.4791, 168.6243, 167.9539, 168.8264, 170.3125, 169.7567, 169.4596, 169.3098, 170.1046, 170.5635, 171.7044, 171.4437, 170.8153, 170.4999, 170.7617, 170.9057, 170.3245, 171.7669, 172.5378, 172.1427, 173.166, 174.1645, 172.2266, 171.7711, 172.4472, 171.7406, 171.7117, 171.6585, 173.3792, 172.3395, 172.5497, 172.2255, 171.2093, 174.0005, 174.1176, 173.3243, 172.8815, 172.5394, 173.4275, 173.4754, 171.9833, 172.1292, 172.247, 171.775, 172.0961, 172.5099, 173.6299, 171.8979, 172.3124, 172.2436, 173.149, 173.0366, 172.1405, 172.8874, 171.5874, 172.0668, 171.7604, 169.5265, 169.838, 169.8149, 170.1923, 168.8647, 168.6965, 167.7088, 167.9367, 168.3097, 167.9974, 168.5811, 167.5646, 167.8776, 168.2206, 167.2365, 167.7404, 166.967, 165.8807, 164.9132, 165.6374, 167.6051, 168.3867, 167.7551, 168.4966, 168.2802, 168.7693, 168.4359, 168.0478, 169.0712, 169.4039, 169.7781, 170.7559, 171.505, 170.7604, 170.7398, 171.4167, 171.3708, 171.1096, 171.6717, 171.5272, 172.3371, 172.1089, 172.7606, 173.1772, 172.9667, 172.6279, 173.8186, 173.3738, 172.4674, 172.4241, 172.5906, 173.5007, 173.7657, 175.4598, 175.4093, 176.682, 176.6993, 176.9799, 177.3922, 174.9516, 175.1913, 175.0152, 174.8902, 177.6616, 178.4924, 176.987, 176.3487, 176.9596, 177.7714, 178.41, 177.3601, 176.294, 176.2031, 175.4819, 176.6419, 176.5772, 175.9459, 174.8901, 174.0312, 172.1002, 172.8198, 173.2448, 173.0508, 172.7336, 171.4269, 171.8867, 166.449, 164.0284, 163.6833, 163.1831, 160.3151, 164.6237, 170.3145, 166.7192, 164.9881, 169.912, 170.0721, 167.5592, 168.2711, 165.8858, 167.991, 167.9368, 165.7256, 164.598, 167.6252, 166.7883, 166.2393, 168.1318, 167.3531, 166.6682, 165.1494, 162.88, 163.9113, 161.7902, 161.7027, 161.7192, 161.7579, 161.9414, 161.0676, 164.8402, 165.2136, 165.5486, 165.5982, 165.9038, 166.6667, 166.6236, 164.5115, 165.0611, 165.0973], "summary_html": "<h1>规则型基本面择时因子 | Sharpe 0.98 | 通过</h1>\n<h2>策略概述</h2>\n<p>将量价技术指标的规则型构造方式（布林带、分位数通道）迁移到基本面数据（库存/仓单、利润、基差）上，形成规则型基本面择时因子。核心思想是：基本面数据的高低水平可以用统计通道量化，当基本面指标偏离历史常态（突破通道上下轨或处于极端分位数位置）时，发出择时信号。两个单因子可通过 AND 逻辑组合，降低开仓频率和回撤风险。</p>\n<h2>回测表现</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>指标</th><th>值</th></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (全期, 4bps)</td><td><strong>0.9</strong></td></tr><tr><td>年化收益</td><td>2.6%</td></tr><tr><td>年化波动</td><td>2.9%</td></tr><tr><td>最大回撤</td><td>-4.1%</td></tr><tr><td>日均换手</td><td>0.03</td></tr><tr><td>回测天数</td><td>3450</td></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (样本内 2016-2025)</td><td><strong>1.15</strong></td></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (样本外 2025+)</td><td><strong>0.24</strong></td></tr><tr><td>半样本 H1/H2</td><td>1.1 / 1.21</td></tr></table></div>\n<p><strong>年度 Sharpe</strong>:</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>年份</th><th>2015</th><th>2016</th><th>2017</th><th>2018</th><th>2019</th><th>2020</th><th>2021</th><th>2022</th><th>2023</th><th>2024</th><th>2025</th><th>2026</th></tr><tr><td>Sharpe</td><td>0.13</td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-0.13</span></td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">2.15</span></td><td>0.85</td><td>1.0</td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">2.94</span></td><td>1.3</td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">2.31</span></td><td>0.15</td><td>0.5</td><td>0.18</td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-1.14</span></td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>数据字段依赖</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>字段</th><th>说明</th><th>必需</th></tr><tr><td><code>close</code></td><td>收盘价</td><td>是</td></tr><tr><td><code>receipt</code></td><td>仓单</td><td>是</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>信号更新频率</h2>\n<ul><li><strong>数据频率</strong>: 日频</li>\n<li><strong>调仓周期</strong>: 每 10 个交易日</li>\n<li><strong>信号更新</strong>: 每日计算，每 10 天生效</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>品种覆盖</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>指标</th><th>值</th></tr><tr><td>覆盖品种数</td><td>59</td></tr><tr><td>回测交易日</td><td>3452</td></tr><tr><td>非零仓位占比</td><td>84.9%</td></tr><tr><td>日均持仓品种</td><td>44.9</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>数学公式</h2>\n<p><strong>滚动分位数信号</strong>：</p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">P_t = \frac{X_t - \\min_{s \\in [t-N, t]} X_s}{\\max_{s \\in [t-N, t]} X_s - \\min_{s \\in [t-N, t]} X_s}</div>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">ext{signal}_t = \begin{cases} -1 &amp; \text{if } P_t &gt; q_{\text{upper}} \text{ (累库/高利润 → 看空)} \\\\ +1 &amp; \text{if } P_t &lt; q_{\text{lower}} \text{ (去库/低利润 → 看多)} \\\\ \text{signal}_{t-1} &amp; \text{otherwise (persistent)} \\end{cases}</div>\n<p><strong>AND 组合逻辑</strong>：</p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">ext{combo}_t = \begin{cases} +1 &amp; \text{if signal}^A_t = +1 \text{ AND signal}^B_t = +1 \\\\ -1 &amp; \text{if signal}^A_t = -1 \text{ AND signal}^B_t = -1 \\\\ 0 &amp; \text{otherwise} \\end{cases}</div>\n<p>其中 <span class=\"math-tex\">X_t</span> 为基本面指标值（receipt/profit/basis），<span class=\"math-tex\">N</span> 为回看窗口，<span class=\"math-tex\">q</span> 为分位数阈值。</p>\n<h2>改进历程</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>轮次</th><th>诊断</th><th>行动</th><th>效果</th></tr><tr><td>R1</td><td>Sharpe=-0.23, 所有变体为负。原因：使用 inventory_lp（已处理指标，非原始库存），且基差方向设为 negative（应为 positive）</td><td>改用 receipt（仓单原始数据）作为库存代理；修正基差方向为 positive（高基差=backwardation→看多期货）</td><td>Sharpe 从 -0.23 → 0.87</td></tr><tr><td>R2</td><td>Sharpe=0.87 通过阈值。但 Bollinger 方法全品种表现差（负 Sharpe），仅 percentile 方法有效</td><td>聚焦分位数方法，增加窗口/阈值/hold_days 参数网格搜索（13 个变体）</td><td>Sharpe 从 0.87 → 0.98，10 个变体 &gt; 0.8</td></tr><tr><td>R3</td><td>252 天长窗口 + 截面标准化 (_cs) 为最优组合。TS ICIR 达 0.29</td><td>最终确认</td><td>Sharpe 0.98, all gates pass</td></tr></table></div>\n<p><strong>关键转折点</strong>：R1→R2 的数据字段修正是决定性的。inventory_lp 是经过处理的多空指标而非原始库存量，receipt（仓单）才是反映实际库存水平的正确字段。</p>\n<h2>适用说明</h2>\n<ul><li><strong>数据频率</strong>: 日频</li>\n<li><strong>品种范围</strong>: 全商品期货（57 个品种有 receipt 数据）</li>\n<li><strong>持仓周期</strong>: 10 日换仓（persistent 信号，实际持仓更长）</li>\n<li><strong>信号特征</strong>: 低频交易（分位数极值触发），多头时间略多于空头</li>\n<li><strong>已知局限</strong>:</li>\n</ul>  - receipt 数据为周度更新（daily 中 forward-fill），信号变化频率本身较低\n<p>- Bollinger 方法在全品种上表现不佳，仅分位数方法有效 - 基差和利润的分位数因子单独使用效果有限（Sharpe &lt; 0.4） - 年度 Sharpe 不均匀：2020 年最好(0.44)，2025 年为负(-0.23)</p>\n<h2>验证状态</h2>\n<ul><li>corr vs Polars: 1.0</li>\n<li>Pandas 运行时间: 0.29s</li>\n</ul>"}